---
title: White Chocolate Pots with Almond Crumble & Passionfruit Lemon Sauce | Serves 4
description: Creamy, dreamy and decadent, round out your night with these heavenly white choc pots. Leave them with enough time to
set in the fridge, then top with some passionfruit sauce and nutty crumble for the crunch factor.
